name: Low Effort Jam 20 - Turbo Vacuum
description:
This was a quick ~6 hours of low effort programming practice as it's been a good year since I actually did a code.

Move around with WASD and hold down Space to use your super cool and expensive vacuum. Make sure you plug into a white power socket by left clicking one with your mouse first!

You can open and close the upgrade shop with "I". Suck up loads of trash and upgrade your cool new vacuum even further

(You can also press "R" to restart the game if you get stuck)

This was a fun practice to get back into the swing of things, and I feel like with a lot more effort this could be a neat lil game idk :)
